Problem:

Write a program to find x to the power n (i.e. x^n). Take x and n from the user. You need to print the answer.

*******************************************************************************************************************************

Program:

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() {
int x,n;
    cin>>x>>n;
    int i=1,res=1;
    while(i<=n)
    {
        res= res*x;
        i=i+1;
    }
    cout<<res;
}

*******************************************************************************************************************************

Output:

Sample Input:
 3 4
Sample Output:
81

